<doc docid='voa_5326138' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/5326138.html' term='COVID'>
Soomaaliya oo ‘4 muwaadin u karantiishay’ Coronavirus
Dowladda Soomaaliya ayaa sheegtay in jiraan afar muwaadin oo Soomaali ah oo ka yimid dalka Shiinaha, oo ay u karantiileen si ay u xaqiijiyaan inay ka bed qabaan fayruska Coronavirus ee dunida faraha ba’an ku haya.
War-saxaafadeed ka soo baxay wasaaradda caafimaadka ayaa lagu sheegay in afartaasi qof ay galeen Soomaaliya 10-kii iyo 11-kii Maarso 2020, laguna hakiyay gegida diyaaradaha ee Aadan Cabdulle.
Dadkaas ayaa sida ay wasaaradda sheegtay kadib loo gudbiyey goob gaar ah oo lagu haynayo inta ay ka dhamaasanyaan mudadada xilli-huuriska ee loogu tala galay in la haayo dadka soo maray meelo uu ka jiro cudurka COVID-19.
Wasaaraddu waxey sheegtay in dadkaasi ay ka qaaday dheecaanno si baaritaan loogu diro looguna soo sameeyo dalka dibaddiisa.
Waxey sheegtay in ilaa iyo hadda aysan dadkaasi ka muuqan wax calaamada ah oo muujinaya inay qabaan cudurka COVID-19, isla markaana aanu jirin welwel laga qabo, laakiin ay marsiinayaan habraaca hubinta.
Ugu danbayntii, wasaaradda caafimaadka ayaa kula talinaysay dhamaan dadka kasoo safraya waddamada uu ka jiro feyruskan inay hakiyaan safarada ay ku imanayaan Soomaaliya.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_5328884' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/5328884.html' term='COVID'>
Somaliland: Waan u Diyaar-garownay ka Hortagga Coronavirus
Iyadoo kiisaskii ugu horreeyey ee xanuunka coronavirus ee loo yaqaano COVID 19 ay soo weriyeen dalalka Bariga Africa sida Kenya iyo Ethiopia ayaa wasaaradda Caafimaadka ee Somaliland waxa ay mar kale ka warbixisay sida ay ugu diyaargaroobeen ka hortagista xanuunkan dunida faraha ba’an ku haya.
Wariyaha VOA, Sagal Mustafe Xassan ayaa arrimahan ka wareysatay Wasiirka Wasaaradda Caafimaadka ee Somaliland Cumar Cali Cabdullaahi.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_5330597' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/5330597.html' term='COVID'>
Somalia oo laga helay CoronaVirus, iyo duulimaadyada oo la joojiyey
MUQDISHO —
Dawladda Soomaaliya ayaa xaqiijisay in qof Soomaali ah markii ugu horraysay laga helay cudurka CoronaVirus.
Wasiirka Caafimaadka Soomaaliya Fowsiya Abiikar Nuur ayaa sheegtay in kiiskan laga helay qof Soomaali ah oo ka yimid dibedda, qofkaasi oo lagu hayo meel gaar ah.
Dawladda Soomaaliya waxay sheegtay in qofka laga jelay uu ka yimid mid ka mid ah waddamada laga helaya cudurka COVID-19.
Dawladda Soomaaliya ayaa sidoo kale sheegtay inay diyaarisay cisbitaal haddii ay xaalado soo baxaan lagu daaweeyo.
Wasiirka caafimaadka ayaa ugu baaqday dadka Soomaalida inay is dejiyaan.
Wasiirka duulista hawada Maxamed Cabdullaahi Oomaar ayaa isna sheegay inay dawladdu joojisya dhammana duulimaadyada caalamiga ah ee yimaada kana baxa dalka, laga bilaabo 18-ka bisha Maarso muddo 15 maalmood ah.
Amarkan ayaa saamaynaya ilaa 15 diyaaradood oo yimaada Soomaaliya oo ay ku jiraan kuwa qaadka iyo kuwa rakaabka.
Hoos ka dhageys codka Fowsiya
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_5322455' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/5322455.html' term='COVID'>
Trump lagama baarin Coronavirus - Aqalka Cad
Aqalka Cad ee Mareykanka ayaa Isniintii sheegay in madaxweyne Donald Trump aan laga baarin cudurka Coronavirus, inkasta looga cabsi qabo dad uu xiriir la sameeyey.
Laba sharci-dejiye oo ka tirsan Aqalka Wakiilada Mareykanka, oo Trump uu xiriir la sameeyey, ayaa dhowaan sheegay inay si iskood ah isku karantiilayaan kadib markii ay ka qeyb galeen shir uu sidoo kale joogay qof laga helay cudurka.
“Madaxweyne Trump lagama baarin cudurka COVID-19, sababtoo ah ma jirin xiriir waqti dheer ah oo uu la sameeyey qof la xaqiijiyey inuu cudurka qabo, mana lahan wax astaamo cudurka ah,” ayaa lagu yiri bayaan ay soo saartay afhayeenka Aqalka Cad Stephanie Grisham.
“Madaxweynaha caafimaadkiisa aad ayuu u wanaagsan yahay, waxaana kormeer kusii wadi doona dhaqtarkiisa.”
Xubnaha sheegay inay is-karantiilayaan waxaa ka mid ah madaxa cusub ee Shaqaalaha Aqalka Cad Mark Meadows oo sheegay in laga yaabo inuu xiriir la sameeyey qof la xaqiijiyey inuu cudurkan ku dhacay.
Waxaa sidoo kale sheegay inay is-karantiilayaan Senator Ted Cruz iyo saddex xubnood oo kale oo ka tirsan Aqalka Wakiilada oo kala ah Paul Gosar, Doug Collins iyo Matt Gaetz, kuwaas oo dhammaantood sheegay inay xiriir la sameeyeen qof laga helay cudurka oo ka qeyb-galay shir ay ku sugnaayeen.
34 ka mid ah gobollada Mareykanka iyo magaalada caasimadda ah ee Washington DC ayaa laga helay kiisas la xiriirka cudurka Coronavirus.
Jaamacadda Johns Hopkins ayaa Isniintii sheegtay in guud ahaan caalamka laga xaqiijiyey 113,584 kiis oo cudurka Coronavirus ah, iyo dhimashada 3,996, kuwaas oo badankood Shiinaha ah.
REUTERS
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_5319238' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/5319238.html' term='COVID'>
Masaajidada Mareykanka iyo Coronovirus
Dalaka Mareykanka waxaa ku sii faafaya xanuunka Coronavirus ama COVID 19.
Haddii uu sii socdo faafista canuunkan waxaa dhici karta inuu saameyn ku yeesho goobaha ay bulshada isugu yimaadaan.
Meelaha isha sida gaarka ah loogu hayo waxaa ka mida goobaha cibaadada.
Haddaba, sidee masaajidada dalkan Mareykanka ku yaalla ay arrintan u wajahayaan? Falastiin Axmed Iiman ayaa ka wareysatay Sheikh Cabdiraxmaan Shariif oo ah imaamka Masaajidka Daarul-Hijra ee Magaalada Minneapolis.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_5330324' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/5330324.html' term='COVID'>
Waxyeelada COVID-19 ee gobolka Washington
Xilli tirada dadka uu soo ridanayo Corona Virus ee gudaha Mareyakanka ay sii kordhayaan ayaa haddana waxaa socda dadaallo dowladda Mareykanka ay kula tacaalayso sidii loo xakameyn lahaa Vruska.
Dhimashada ugu badan ee sababay Corona Virus ee gudaha Mareykanka ayaa ka dhacday Gobolka Washington oo Soomaal badan ay ku noolyihiin, kaas oo hadda kujira xaalad dag dag ah oo maamulka gobolkaasi uu kusoo rogay
Wariyaha VOAda Cabdulqaadir Samakaab ayaa khadka telefonka kula xiriiray madaxa Hay’adda Somali Health Board Dr Maxamed Aadan Cali oo ku sugan magaalada Seattle ee gobolka Washington, waxuuna marka hore wediiyay sida hadda uu xaalku yahay.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_5280508' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/5280508.html' term='SARS'>
Dadka uu Dilay Coronavirus oo Kor u Dhaafaya 800 oo Qof
Afar qof oo la socday markabka dalxiiska ee Royal Caribbean ayaa magaalada Newark ee gobolka New Jersey lagu qiimeynayaa suurtagalnimada ah in ay qabaan xanuunka Coronavirus ee ka dillaacay dalka China. 11 qof oo kale oo Mareykan ah ayaa karantiil ahaan ugu jira markab kale oo ku sugan xeebta dalka Japan oo laga helay xanuunka.
Dhanka kale, dhakhtarkii sameeyay qaylo dhaanta la xiriirta fayraska coronavirus ayaa u dhintay cudurkan iyada oo la xaqiijiyey in kiisaska dadka uu ku dhacay xanuunka ay ka badan yihiin 31,000.
Tirada dadka dhuntay firus-kan coronavirus kor u dhaaftay 800 oo qof oo ku dhintay gudaha dalka Shiinaha.
Wakaaladda Wararka ee AFP ayaa ka soo xigatay saraakiisha caafimaadka in tirada dadka ku dhintay firus-kan ay haatan kor u dhaaftay tirada dadkii uu dilay firus-kii SARS ee sanadihii 2002 ilaa 2003-dii dad gaaraya 774 qof ku dilay qeybo badan oo caalamka ah.
Weriyaha VOA Mariama Diallo ayaa warbixintan ka diyaarisay, Caasha Ibraahim Aadan ayaana soo koobeysa.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_1914102' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/1914102.html' term='MERS'>
Xanuunka MERS oo America laga Helay
Laba qof oo mareykan ah ayaa laga helay xanuunka neef-wareenka bariga dhexe ee (MERS), kuwaas oo la sheegay in ay ka so noqdeen Saudi Arabia, iyadoo aad looga cabsi qabo in uu xanuunku fido.
Bariga dhexe ayaa dad badan xanuunkaasi ugu dhinteen.
Dr. Maxamed Cabdullahi Xaji Aden oo ku takhasusay xanuunada gudaha kana shaqeeyay Regions Hospital ee gobolka Minnesota ayaa VOA-da uga warramay xanuunkan.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2483297' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2483297.html' term='ebola'>
Obama oo Madaxda Caalamka Kala Hadlay Ebola
Madaxweynaha Maraykanka Obama oo khadka tilifoonka kula hadlay Xoghayaha Guud ee Qaramada Midoobay Ban Ki Moon ayaa sheegay inay ku heshiiyeen in baahi loo qabo in lala yimaaddo ballanqaadyo adag iyo weliba taakulo degdeg ah oo loo diro wadamada Galbeedka Afrika ku yaalla si loo joojiyo fiditaanka Ebola.
Madaxweyne Obama oo ay sidoo kale khadka telefoonka ku wada xidhiidheen Madaxweynaha dalka Faransiiska ayay ka wada hadleen in la qaado tallaabooyin isku xidhan si loo xakameeyo faafista cudurkan, tallaabooyinkaas oo ay ku jiraan in galbeedka Afrika laga hirgeliyo goobo lagu daaweeyo dadka xanuunkani ku dhaco iyo weliba in la baadho caafimaadka dadka raacaya diyaaradaha ee gobolkaas ka soo safraya.
Madaxweyne Obama sidoo kale macluumaad laga siiyey jawaabta laga bixiyey habka loola tacaalay bukaankii labaad ee uu xanuunka Ebola ku dhaco gudaha dalka Maraykanka oo ah kalkaaliso caafimaad oo ku sugan gobolka Texas, waxyaabaha madaxweynaha lagu wargeliyey ama macluumaadka laga siiyey waxaa ku jira baadhitaan la xidhiidha sida ay u dhacday iyadoo la raacayo anshaxa caafimaadka iyo ka feejignaanta in haddana ay suuro gashay in mid ka mida shaqaalihii caafimaadka laga helo xanuunkan.
Warbaahinta ayaa ogaatay in bukaanka xanuunkani ku dhacay ay ahayd kalkaaliso caafimaad oo 26 jir ah laguna magcaabo, taas oo daryeel caafimaad u fidisay nin u dhashay dalka Liberia oo xanuunkan ugu geeriyooday gudaha dalka Maraykanka, xilligan waxaa xaaladeeda caafimaad lagula tacaalayaa goob gaar ah, xaaladeeda caafimaadna waa mid deggan.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2460681' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2460681.html' term='ebola'>
Waraysi Gaar ah: Wasiirka Arrimaha Africa ee Britain
Wasiirka Britain ee Arrimaha Afrika ayaa sheegay inay lagama maarmaan tahay in Somalia ay ka dhacdo doorasho sannadka 2016 si waddanka uu horey ugu talaabsado.
Mr James Duddridge oo bishii horey qabtey xafiiska ayaa sidoo kale ka Hadley dadaalka loogu jiro la dagaalanka Ebola, xasaradda ka aloosan Koonfurta Sudan, ururrada xagjirka ee ka jira Africa iyo arrimo kale.
Weriyaha VOA Daud Aweis ayaa wareysi gaar ah Mr Duddridge kula yeeshey xarunta Qaramada Midoobay ee New York.
Warbixinta oo dhammaystiran ka dhegayso qaybta hoose ee boggan.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_1967817' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/1967817.html' term='ebola'>
Cudurka Ebola oo ku sii Fidiya Sierra Leone
In ka badan 10 kun oo qof ayaa isugu soo baxay caasimada Liberia ee Monrovia iyaga oo ka soo horjeeda in deegaankooda laga furo xarun lagu karantiilo dadka uu ku dhaco cudurka Ebola, hasa yeeshee wasaarada caafimaadka ee Liberiya ayaa sheegtay in xaruntu ay muhiim u tahay in lagula dagaalamo in cudurku uu faafo, iyadoo dadka reer Liberia ay u baahan yihiin in ay aaminaan shaqaalaha caafimaadka.
Haddaba cudurka Ebola oo dad badan ay qaadeen dalal ku yaala galbeedka Afrika, aadna u fidaya ayaa Ibrahim Hassan Daandurey uu khadka telefoonka kula xiriiray Dr. Mohamed Abdullahi Hagi Aden oo ku takhasusay daweeynta xanuunada gudaha, kana shaqeeya cusbitaalka Regions Hospital oo ku yaala magaalada S.Paul ee gobolka Minnisota, wuxuuna ugu horeyn weydiiya waxa keena cudurka.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2460322' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2460322.html' term='ebola'>
Shirka Golaha Guud Ee Qaramada Midoobay
In ka badan 140 madaxweyne ayaa ku sugan magaalada New York ee dalkan Mareykanka, halkaas oo uu shalay ka furmay shirkii 69aad ee sanadlaha ee Golaha Guud ee loo dhanyahay ee Qaramada Midoobay.
Ajendayaasha shirka sanadkan ayaa waxaa hareeyay khudbooyin iyo wada hadalo ku saabsan mushkiladaha cusub ee dunida soo wajahay, sida cudurka dilaaga ah ee Ebola, dagaalka ka dhanka ah kooxda Daacish, dagaalka Ukraine, ka hortagista faafidda hubka Nukliyeerka iyo Cimiliada sii kululaaneysa ee Dunida.
Maanta ayaa waxaa shirka Khudbado ka jeedin doona madaxweynayaasha dalalk xubnaha ka ah Qaramada Midoobay.
iyadoo dhinaca kale, qodobada shirka maanta looga hadlayo ay ku jirto Somalia.
Wariyeheena Daud Aweys oo shirkaasi u jooga New York ayaa nooga soo waramay.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_4401877' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/4401877.html' term='ebola'>
DRC: Cudurka Ebola oo Dad Hor leh Dilay
Wasaaradda caafimaadka Congo ayaa sheegtay in qof cusub uu maanta u geeriyooday xanuunka Ebola. Tirada guud ee dadka u dhintay cudurkaasi oo ku faafay gobolka Equateur ee galbeedka dalkaasi waxa ay gaareysaa 26 ruux.
Waxaa la xaqiijiyay in 4 qof oo cusub oo ku dhaqan dalka Congada Dimuqraadiga ah uu xanuunkaasi haleelay, sida lagu xusay bayaan kasoo baxay wasaaradda Caafimaadka dalkaasi.
Ilaa 46 ruux ayay soo ridatay qandhada la yiraahdo hemorrhagic, waxaana la xaqiijiyay in 21 kamid ahi ay qabaan Ebola, 21 kalena loo badinayo, halka 4-ta soo hartayna looga shakisan yahay.
Madaxweynaha dalkaasi Joseph Kabila iyo golihiisa wasiirrada ayaa sabtidii go'aamiyay in la kordhiyo lacagta loo qorsheeyay in dag dag wax looga qabto cudurkaasi oo gaareysa ilaa 4 milyan oo doollar.
Waa markii 9aad oo uu cudurka Ebola ka dillaaco dalkaasi Congo muddo 40 sano ah, hase yeeshee kuwii hore waxa ay ku koobnaayeen dhulka miyiga ah. Laba jeer ayuu ku dhiftay caasimadda dalkaasi ee Kinshasa oo dadka ku nooli ay 10 milyan gaarayaan, hase yeeshee si dag dag ah ayuu ku joogsaday
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2411901' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2411901.html' term='ebola'>
WHO: Dawada Ebola Degdeg Haloo Adeegsado
Hay’adda Caafimaadka Aduunka ee marka magaceeda la soo gaabiyo la yiraa WHO ayaa sheegtay inay arin saxan tahay in dadka uu soo rito xanuunka EBOLA lagula tacaalo dawooyinka aan weli tijaabadoodu dhamaan, si loola dagaalamo Faafista Viruska ee galbeedka Africa.
Hadalkan WHO ayaa soo baxay, xilli saraakiisha caafimaadka ee Liberia ay filayeen inay dawo lagu tijaabinayo dadka Ebola la xanuunsan ka helaan shirkad Mareykanka laga leeyahay.
Dawadan oo loo bixiyay ZMapp, weli laguma tijaabin bani aadam.
In ka badan 1,000 qocf ayaa Ebola u geeriyooday tan iyo markii uu ka dilaacay galbeedka Africa bishii February, dadkaas oo badankood ku dhintay Guinea, Liberia iyo Sierra Leone.
Hadaba si aan wax uga ogaano dawadan cusub iyo saameynta Ebola waxaan khadka taleefanka ee magaalada London kula xiriirnay Dr. Mohamed Xaaji Abdullahi oo ka howlgala xarun caafimaad oo ku taala Totenham.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_4385858' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/4385858.html' term='ebola'>
Cudurka Ebola oo mar kale ka dillaacay Congo
WASHINGTON. D.C —
Dowlada Jamhuuriyadda Dimoqraadiga Congo ayaa ku dhawaaqday inuu dalkeeda mar kale ka dillaacay cudurka Ebola.
17 ruux oo dhawaan dalkaasi ku geeriyooday ayay dowladu sheegtay in looga shakiyay kiisas la xiriira caabuqa Ebola. Laba ka mid ah dadka dhintay ayaa la xaqiijiyay in uu cudurkani dilay,
Hey’adda Caafimaadka Aduunka ee WHO ayaa Talaadadi shalay sheegtay in Congo uu haleelay cudurka Ebola, sidaasi daraadeedna ay hal milyan oo doolar oo deg deg ah ku tabarucday si ay ugu caawiso gagrgaar deg deg ah.
WHO waxay sheegtay in shanti todobaad ee lasoo dhaafay laga helay dalkaasi kiisaska 21 ruux deegaanka Bikoro ee gobolka Equateur.
Marki ugu danbeysay ee uu cudurkani ka dillaacay Congo ayay aheyd sanadki 2017-ki. Waa marki sagaalaad oo uu cudurka Ebola ka dillaacayo aduunka tan iyo marki ugu horreysay ee la ogaado sanadki 1976-ki.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_3048016' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/3048016.html' term='ebola'>
WHO: Cudurka Ebola Kama Jiro Sierra Leone
Dadweynaha ku nool dalka Sierra Leone ayaa si aad ah u sugayey in markii uu lagu dhawaaqo in cudurkaasi uusan dalka ka jiran kuwaasoo xannuun ka soo maray jirtaanka cudurkaasi kaddib markii uu galaaftay nolosha 4,000 kun oo qof sanadihii la soo dhaafay.
Abdulla Bayraytay, oo ah isku-duwaha arrimaha wacyigelinta arrimaha bulshada ee qaranka ayaa sheegay in daafaha kala duwan ee dalka Sierra Leone laga sameyn doono maalin dabaal-dag ah, taasoo lagu xusidoono dadkii uu galaaftay cudurka Ebola iyo dhakhaatiirta dadaalka badan u sameysan sidii cudurkaasi lola dagaalami lahaa.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_1972164' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/1972164.html' term='ebola'>
Liberia oo la Tacaaleysa Cudurka Ebola
Mas’uuliyiinta dalka Liberia ayaa la tacaalaya kororka meydadka dadka u dhintey xanuunka Ebola kuwaas oo aan weli la aasin kuna dayacan xaafadaha iyo tuulooyinka uu ka dilaacay virus-ka dhaliya Ebola.
Warbaahinta maxalliga ayaa sheegaya in xarrumaha caafimaadka oo ay dad buux dhaafiyeen awgeed ay horseedday in meydadka lagu dayaco xaafadaha muddo dhowr maalmood ah.
Wararka ayaa sheegaya in 37 meyd ah laga heley maalintii Axadda goob ku taalla magaalada caasimadda ah ee Monrovia.
Wasiirka Warfaafinta ee Liberia Lewis Brown ayaa VOA u sheegay in hay’adaha caafimaadka qaarkood aaney horey ugu diyaargaroobin xaaladaha ay la iman kareen bulshooyinka waddankaasi ku dhaqan.
Waxaa uu sheegay in bulshada qaarkeed ay diiddan yihiin in degaannadooda lagu aaso dadka uu cudurkan aafeeyey.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2761045' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2761045.html' term='ebola'>
Liberia oo Laga Cidhib-tiray EBOLA
Laanta Caafimaadka Adduunka ee WHO ayaa ku dhawaaqday in dalka Liberia laga cidhib tiray xanuunka Ebola.
WHO ayaa hadalkan ku dhawaaqday ka dib markii aan dalkaas lagu arkin cid xanuunka qabta muddo 42 maalmood ah, oo ah laban laab xilliga la fili karo in xanuunkaasi qofka soo rito.
Laakiin weli wadamada galbeedka Afrika ayaa xanuunkaasi ka jiraa, gaar ahaan dalalka Sierra Leone iyo Guinea oo deris la ah Liberia taas oo toddobaadkii hore lagu soo waramay in lagu arkay dal kasta illaa 9 qof.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_5026291' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/5026291.html' term='ebola'>
Congo: Dad hor leh oo laga helay Ebola
Xarunta Xakameynta Cudurrada ayaa ku warantay in ay shaqaale toban ka badan u dirtay magaalo ku taalla xuduudda dalka Jamhuuriyadda Dimoqraadiga ah ee Congo iyo Rwanda si ay u mareeyaan dadka uu cudurka Ebola halkaasi ku haleelay.
Xanuunkan oo sanad kahor dalkaasi ka dillaacay ayaa galaaftay nolosha dad ka badan 1800. Hey'adda ayaa sheegtay in ay shaqaale kale oo dheraad ah diri doonto haddii uu qaboobo dagaalka ka socda gobolka waqooyi bari ee dalkaasi.
12 kamid ah shaqaalaha Xarunta Xakameynta Cudurka ayaa loo diray magaalada Goma oo ah magaalo halbowle u ah u-kala-gooshidda dalalka Congo iyo Rwanda. Goma ayaa laga helay qofkii afaraad oo uu Ebola soo rito.
Hey'adda Caafimaadka Adduunka ayaa sheegtay in qof afaraad uu xanuunkan kusoo rito magaaladaasi soohdinta ku taalla ay walaac xooggan abuureyso.
Agaasimaha Xarnta Xakameynta Xanuunka Ebola Dr. Robert Radfield ayaa bartiisa Twitter-ka ku sheegay in iska-hor-iaamdyada hubeysani ay curyaaminayaan dadaallada saraakiisha caafimaadka ee ku howlan joojinta faafista cudurka, taasoo buu yiri sare usii qaadeysa halista sii faafiddiisa.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_4846556' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/4846556.html' term='ebola'>
Kiisas Cusub oo Cudurka Ebola oo Laga Helay DRC
Koox caalami ah oo gargaarka ka shaqeysa ayaa sheegtay in 58 kiis o cusub oo cudurka ebolaha ah laga helay Jamhuuriyadda Dimuquraadiga ee Congo todobaadkii tagay – waana tiraddii ugu badneyd ee muddo todobaad ah la soo wariyo sanadkan.
Hey’adda IRC ayaa sheegtay in tirada saxda ah ay intaasi ka badan karto, iyadoo ay ugu wacantahay in dadku aysan soo sheegin kiisas dhacay, sababo la xiriira aminaad darri iyo amaanka.
Hey’addan ayaa intaasi ku dartay in tirada dadka ilaa iyo hadda la xaqiijiyay inuu cudurkaasi soo ritay ay ka badantahay Kun qof, uuna sii socon karo faafista cudurka sanad kale.
Hey’addan ayaa sheegtay inay aheyd todoba bilood ka dib markii uu bilowday dilaacay cudurkan in tiradu ay hoos u dhacdo oo aysan kordhin.
Hey’adda waxey sheegtay in arrintan ay astaan u tahay, inkastoo dadaal xoog leh lagu bixiyay hadana in joogsiga faafista cudurku uusan dhaweyn.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2477808' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2477808.html' term='ebola'>
Cabsi la Xiriirta Ebola oo ka Jirta Australia
Kalkaaliso caafimaad oo u dhalatey Australia ayaa baaritaanno caafimaad lagu sameynayaa kadib markii jirkeeda lagu arkey calaamado ay suuragal tahay inuu hayo xanuunka Ebola, iyadoo beesha caalamka ay ku guda jirto dadaal la doonayo in lagu xakameeyo faafitaanka virus-ka.
Madaxa caafimaadka ee gobolka Queensland Jeanette Young ayaa sheegtay in haweeneydaasi oo 57 jir ah uu xummad ku dhacay wax yar kadib markii ay ka soo laabatey dalka Sierra Leone, halkaas oo ay ku caawineysey bukaan uu ku dhacay xanuunka Ebola.
Natiijada baaritaanka la wado ayaa la filayaa inay soo baxdo maalinta Jimcaha. Young ayaa sidoo kale sheegtay in xitaa haddii haweeneydan la xaqiijiyo inay qabto Ebola aaney jirin sabab ay shacabka walaac uga muujiyaan in virus-ka uu waddanka ku baahayo.
Arrintan ayaa imaneysa maalin kadib markii qofkii ugu horeeyey ee gudaha Mareykanka lagu ogaado inuu ku dhacay Ebola uu ku geeriyooday magaalada Dallas ee gobolka Texas.
Saraakiisha isbitalka Texas Health Presbyterian ayaa sheegay in Thomas Eric Duncan uu dhintey 10 maalmood kadib markii isbitalkaasi la dhigey. Waxaa uu Dallas yimid bishii September 20-keeda isagoo ka yimid Liberia oo oo ah waddanka uu u dhashey, kana mid ah waddamada Galbeedka Afrika ee sida ba’an uu u aafeeyey Ebola.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_1950605' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/1950605.html' term='ebola'>
Shir Looga Hadley Xanuunka Ebola oo ka Dhacay Ghana
Sarkaal sare oo dhinaca caafimaadka ugu qaabilsan Qaramada Midoobay ayaa sheegay in faafitaanka cudurka Ebola ee ka dilaacay Galbeedka Afrika uu sii socon karo dhowr bilood oo kale.
Keiji Fukuda ayaa wakaaladda wararka Faransiiska ee AFP u sheegay inaaney suuragal ahayn in si cad loo saadaaliyo xaddiga uu cudurkan ku sii faafi karo.
Mr Fukuda waxaa uu hadalkan ka jeediyey dalka Ghana markii halkaasi lagu soo gabagabeeyey shir deg deg ah oo laba maalmood socdey oo ay yeesheen wasiirada caafimaadka ee qaaradda Afrika iyo khubaro kale. Cudurkan ayaa ilaa iyo haatan dad gaaraya 467 ku diley waddamada Guinea, Liberia, iyo Sierra Leone.
Wasiirrada ayaa shirka ku soo bandhigey dhowr qodob oo talo soo jeedin ah. Waxaa ka mid ah in bulshada la wacyigeliyo, in hoggaamiyeyaasha diinta iyo kuwa siyaasadda ay dadka ku wacyigeliyaan arrimaha xanuunkan, isla markaana lacag hor leh la geliyo barnaamijyada lagula dagaalamayp xanuunka Ebola.
Wasiirrada caafimaadka ee Afrika ayaa sheegay in cudurka Ebola uu khatar ku yahay dhamaan dalalka ku yaalla gobolka iyo meelo ka sii fog intaba.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2682026' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2682026.html' term='ebola'>
UK oo Safiir Cusub Somalia u Magacowday
Boqoradda Britain Queen Elizabth ayaa safiir cusub u magacowday Soomaaliya. Safiirka cusub waxaa lagu magacaabaa Harriet Mathews, waxayna beddelaysaa safiirkii hore Niel Wigan.
Harriet Mathews waa xeel dheere aqoon u leh arrimaha Africa, iyadoo madax ka soo noqotay xafiiska wasaaradda Arrimaha Dibedda Britain u qaabilsan bariga iyo Galbeedka Africa.
Sidoo kale Harriet Mathews waxay madax u ahayd howshii UK ee la dagaalanka cudurka Ebola.
Harriet ayaa xilka safiirnimo ee Soomaaliya la wareegi doontaa bisha June.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2462546' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2462546.html' term='ebola'>
Obama: Ebola Amniga Dunida ayuu Halis ku Yahay
Madaxweynaha Maraykanka Barack Obama ayaa sheegay in virus-ka cudurka Ebola uu si xawli ugu faafayo dalalka Guinea, Liberia, and Sierra Leone.
Obama oo ka hadlayay shir gaar ah oo ku saabsan cudurka Ebola oo dhacay xarunta QM ee New York, ayaa sheegay in cudurkani uu dili karo boqolaal kun oo qof bilaha soo socda.
Madaxweynaha Maraykanka Barack Obama ayaa sheegay in dunidu aysan wax ku filan ka sameynayn sida loo joojinayo cudurka Ebola ee ka jira Galbeedka Africa.
Obama ayaa sheegay in cudurkani uu halis dhinaca amniga ah ku yahay gobolka Galbeedka Africa sidoo kalena halis ku noqon karo dunida inteeda kale.
Saraakiisha caafimaadka Maraykanka ayaa ka digay in cudurka Ebola uu ku dhici karo in kabadan hal malyuun oo qof dhammaadka sannadka danbe.
Obama ayaa u sheegay madaxda caalamka baahida loo qabo inay ka dhabeeyaan balanqaadkooda, sidoo kalena bixiyaan gar-gaar, ay ku jiraan gaadiidka cirka, shaqaalaha caafimaadka iyo qalabka caafimaadka.
Obama ayaa sheegay joojinta cudurka Ebola ay tahay mid ay mudnaan siinayaan dowladda Maraykanku, wuxuuna sheegay in dalalka kalena ay sidaasi oo kale mudnaan siiyaan.
Madaxweyne Obama wuxuu madaxda Liberia, Sieera Leone, Guinea iyo qeybaha kale ee galbeedka Afrika ku amaanay dagaalka ay ku la jiraan cudurkan, isagoo u sheegay inaysan kaligood ahayn.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2409442' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2409442.html' term='ebola'>
Nigeria oo Dad Kale Laga Heley Ebola
Wasaaradda Caafimaadka ee Nigeria ayaa xaqiijisey in qof kale laga heley virus-ka Ebola, magaalada Lagos, taasina ay tirada guud ee dadka uu ku dhacay cudurkan guud ahaan Nigeria ka dhigeysa 10.
Nigeria, Liberia, Guinea iyo Sierra Leone ayaa in muddo ahba dadaal ugu jirey sidii ay u xakameyn lahaayeen virus-ka, laakiin kaabeyaasha caafimaadka iyo nadaafadda oo aad u liidata ayaa ah caqabadda ugu weyn ee hortaagan dadaaladaasi.
Maalintii Sabtida Guinea waxay ku dhawaaqdey inay xireyso xudduudaha ay la leedahay waddamada Liberia iyo Sierra Leone.
Hay’adda Caafimaadka Adduunka ee WHO ayaa faafitaanka cudurkan ku tilmaantey inay tahay xaalad caafimaad oo degdeg ah oo dunida ka dilaacdey.
Agaasimaha Guud ee WHO, Dr. Margaret Chan ayaa sheegtey in afarta dal ee cudurkan uu asiibey ee ku yaalla galbeedka Africa aysan awood u lahayd inay maareeyaan cudurka oo si xawli ah u fidaya, waxaana ay ku baaqdey in kaalmo caalami a
Virus-ka Ebola ee haatan ka dilaacay Galbeedka Africa ayaa u muuqda inay dad badan qaadi doonaan marka la barbardhigo intii jeer ee uu horey cudurka uga dilaacey dunida. Cudurkan ma lahan dawo iyo tallaal toona.
WHO ayaa toddobaadkii hore sheegtey in tirada guud ee dadka uu cudurkan ku asiibey afarta waddan ee Galbeedka Afrika ku yaalla ay gaareyso 1,779 iyadoo 961 ka mid ah ay u dhinteen.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_4946321' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/4946321.html' term='ebola'>
Cudurka Ebola oo fara ba'an ku haya Congo
WASHINGTON. D.C —
Wasaaradda caafimaadka dalka Jamhuuriyadda Dimoqraadiga ah ee Congo ayaa sheegtay in in ka badan 2,000 oo kiis oo la xiriira cudurka dilaaga ah ee Ebola laga helay dalkaasi dhaca bartaha Africa.
Dowladda ayaa sheegtay in cudurka ay ilaa iyo hadda u dhinteen dad gaaraya 1,346, taasoo ka dhigtay tiradi labaad ee ugu badneyd ee uu cudurkani dilo taariikhda.
Isniinti, wasaaradda caafimaadka ee dalka Congo ayaa sheegtay in kaliyah 539 qof laga daweeyay caabuqa keena xanuunkan saf mareenka ah. Taasi ayay wasaaraddu sheegtay in ay ku timid kadib marki horumar laga sameeyay amaanka iyo in cudurka uu ku faafo magaalooyinka.
Wakaaladda wararka AFP ayaa ku warrantay in wali ay maleeshiyo hubeysan khatar ku heyso shaqaalaha caafimaadka ee la tacaalaya cudurka Ebola.
Maleeshiyo hubeysan ayaa dishay shan ka mid ah howlwadeenada caafimaadka dhawaan.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2408577' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2408577.html' term='ebola'>
Cudurka Ebola oo Xawli ku Faafaya
Dalalka Galbeedka Africa ee sida ba’an u saameeyay cudurka Ebola ayaa dadaal adag ugu jira ka hortagga faafitaanka cudurkaasi.
Dawladda Guinea ayaa Sabtidii ku dhawaaqday inay xirtay xadkii ay la lahayd dalka Liberia iyo Sierra Leone.
Saddexdan dal ee deriska ah ayaa waxaa cudurka Ebola u dhintay ugu yaraan kun qof.
Qofkii u dambeeyay ee cudurkan laga helo ayaa ahayd baadariyad u dhalatay dalka Congo oo ka soo qaaday xanuunka kaniisad ay u shaqaynaysay oo ku taalla dalka Liberia.
Dalka Nigeria ayaa ugu yaraan laba qof oo kale waxay u dhinteen cudurkaasi.
Waxaana dalkaasi lagaga dhawaaqay xaalad deg deg ah.
Cudurka Ebola ayaa ku socda xawli aan wali hore loo arag, mana jirto ilaa imika daawo amma tallaal looga hortago.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2580688' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2580688.html' term='ebola'>
Dhacdooyinkii Dunida ee 2014
Waa barnaamij gaar ah oo VOA ka diyaarisay dhacdooyinkii u weynaa ee dunida ka dhacay sannadkii 2014.
Caalamka waxaa sanadkaan 2014 soo maray dhacdooyin kala duwan, kuwaasi oo qaarkood ay ka dhasheen xiisado hor leh oo ilaa imika socda, sida xiisadda Ukraine iyo Ruushka u dhaxaysa
Sidoo kale waxaa sii socday xiisado hore oo aan wali xal loo helin, sida mushkiladda Bariga dhexe oo wali taagan.
Waxa markale soo laba kacleeyay cudurka halista ah ee Ebola oo si xawliya ku faafay dhacdooyin kale.
Qaybta hoose ka dhegayso Barnaamij gaar ah oo arrimahan ka hadlaya:
