<doc docid='voa_2532622' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/ebola-and-west-africa/2532622.html' term='ebola'>
Saamaynta Cudurka Ebola ee Galbeedka Afrika
Xoghayaha Guud ee Qaramada Midoobay ayaa ku dhowaaqay inuu abuuri doono Hawlgal Cusub oo Qaramadada NMidoobay oo Qaabilsan La-dagaalank Cudurka Ebola.
Ban Ki Moon ayaa sheegay inuu xafiiskan ka furi doono dalka Mali, waddankaasi oo toddobaadyadii u dambaysay ay lix qof ugu dhinteen cudurkan.
Haddaba sidee ayaa cudurkan Ebola u saamayeey Gobolka Galbeedka Afrika ee uu halakeeyey? Su’aashaas iyo kuwo kaleba waxaan Haaruun Macruuf uu weydiiyey Prof. Yaxye Sheekh Caamir oo la-taliye u ah Bankiga Adduunka oo toddobaadkan tagay dalka Ghana halkaasi oo uu kaga qaybgalay shir qodobada looga hadlay uu ka mid yahay cudurka Ebola.
Hoos ka dhagayso waraysiga
