<doc docid='voa_2480325' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2480325.html' term='ebola'>
Tirada Dadka Ebola u dhintay oo Korortay
Hey’adda Caafimaadka Aduunka, WHO, ayaa sheegtay in tirada dadka ilaa iyo hadda u dhintay xanuunka Ebola ay korodhay, iyadoo gaartay in ka badan 4 kun oo qof.
WHO ayaa sheegtay Jimcihii shalay in ku dhawaad 8kun iyo 4 boqol oo qof uu ku dhacay viruska la diwaan geliyay ilaa iyo todoba wadan, 4, kun 33 qof oo ka mid ahna ay u dhinteen.
WHO waxey sheegtay in dhamaan dadka cudurka u dhintay ay ku dhinteen dalalka uu sida ba’an u haleelay ee galbeedka Africa, sida Liberia, Sierra Leone iyo Guinea.
Sagaal qof oo kaliya ayaa ku dhintay meelo ka baxsan sadexdaasi dal.
Sideed qof waxey u dhinteen Nigeria halka qofka kalena uu ku dhintay Mareykanka.
Macluumaadka ayaa sidoo kale muujinaya in min hal Keys oo Viruska ah laga helay dalalka Spain iyo Senegal, laakiin aaney qofni ugu dhiman dalalkaasi.
Viruska Ebola oo ka duwan kan dalalkaasi aafeeyay oo ka dilaacay Jamhuuiriyadda Dimuquraadiga Congo ayaa waxaa ku dhintay 43 qof.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_4961972' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/4961972.html' term='ebola'>
Soomaaliya oo ka feejigan cudurka Ebola
Wasaaradda Caafimaadka ee Soomaaliya ayaa sheegtay inaanu jirin walaac ku saabsan in cudurka Ebola uu soo gaar Soomaaliya kadib markii maalmihii lasoo dhaafay laga helay dalka Uganda.
Dalka Kenya ayaa sidoo kale mas’uuliyiintu sheegeen inay baarayaan dhowr qof oo lagu arkay calaamado u eg kuwa Ebola, hase yeeshee mas’uuliyiinta caafimaadku weli ma aysan xaqiijinin.
Dadkaas ayaa si gooni loogu karantiilay kadib markii looga shakiyay inay la xanuunsan yihiin caalaamadaha cudurka waayadaan dambe ku baayay Qaarada Africa ee Ebola, waxaana Sadexdaan qof lagu hayaa Isbitaalka Kericho ee magaalo madaxda Ismaamulka Kericho ee dalka Kenya.
Sahra Cabdi Axmed ayaa arrintan ka waraysatay Wasiir ku xigeenka Caafimaadka Soomaaliya Maxamed Siciid Cabdullaahi.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_1967289' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/1967289.html' term='ebola'>
Cabsi la Xiriirta Faafitaanka Ebola ee Africa
Hay’adaha caafimaadka ayaa isku dayaya inay aqoonsadaan cid kasta oo saarneyd dhowr duulimaad diyaaradeed oo isaga gooshay Galbeedka Afrika toddobaadkii hore, kuwaas oo si uun ula kulmey nin maalmo kadib u dhintey xanuunka Ebola.
Patrick Sawyer ayaa diyaarad ka soo raacey Liberia, waxaana uu habeen baryey dalka Ghana, isagoo kadibna diyaarad kale ka raacey Togo, taas oo ku sii jeedday Nigeria oo ah meesha uu maalintii Jimcaha ugu geeriyoodey xanuunka.
Sawyer ayaa isla markii uu soo gaarey Nigeria lagu xakameeyey goob u gaar ah, laakiin rakaabkii kale ayaa loo oggolaadey inay iska dhaqaaqaan markii lagu wargeliyey in ruux ka mid ah rakaabkii la socdey cudurka Ebola laga heley.
Dad goobjoogeyaal ah ayaa sheegay in Sawyer uu matagey, isla markaana uu shuban haleeley intii uu saarnaa diyaaradaha uu soo raacey midkood.
Laakiin khubarada caafimaadka waxay sheegayaan inaaney taasi ka dhigneyn khatar uu ninkaasi dadkii la soo safrey uu ku qaadsiiyo xanuunka. In la kala qaado virus-ka Ebola ayaa u baahan in qofku gaaro amaba uu taabto dheecaan ka yimaada jirka qofka qaba xanuunkan.
Waxaa mas’uuliyiinka caafimaadka ay is weydiinayaan sababta ninkan oo dhowaan walaashii ay xanuunka Ebola u dhimatey loogu oggolaaadey inuu waddankiisa ka soo dhoofo iyadoo la ogyahay in xanuunkan uu halkaasi ka dilaacey.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2522142' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2522142.html' term='ebola'>
Wadamada G20 oo Goaano ka Gaadhay Dhaqaalaha Dunida
Hoggaamiyayaasha labaatanka waddan ee dunida ugu dhaqaalaha badan ayaa shaaciyey qorshe kor loogu qaadayo waxsoosaarka dakhliga gudaha in ka badan $2 Trillion oo Dollar shanta sano ee soo socota.
Waxaana arrintaasi ku imanaysaa iyada oo maalgelin lagu samaynayo kaabayaasha dhaqaalaha iyo weliba iyada oo kor loo qaadayo ganacsiga xorta ah.
Qoraalka ay sii daayeen hoggaamiyayaashani ayay ku ballanqaadeen inay iskaashi ka sameynayaan sidii ay tallaabo xooggan u qaadi lahaayeen oo ku aaddan isbedelka cimilada dunida, sidoo kale waxay sheegeen inay isla qaateen sidii ay u taageeri lahaayeen dedaallada caalamiga ah ee wax lagaga qabanayo faafista xanuunka Ebola eek a dillaacay galbeedka Afrika.
Ra’iisal wasaaraha Australia Tony Abbot oo ka hadlayey magaalada Brisbane ayaa sheegay in dalalkani ay si dhow uga wadashaqayndoonaan kormeerida iyo hirgelinta ballanqaadyada ay sameeyeen ee kor loogu qaadayo koboca.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_1969059' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/1969059.html' term='ebola'>
AMISOM: Cudurka Ebola Waanu Ka Feejigannahay
Waddanka Siera Leone ayaa ku dhawaaqey xaalad deg deg ah si dalkasi uu ula tacaalo Virus-kii ugu xumaa oo abid ka dilaacay dalkaasi.
Madaxweynaha dalkaasi Leone Ernest Bai Koroma ayaa sheegay in dowladiisu ay karantiileyso deegaano laga helay cudurka, iyadoo dadka loo diidey inay dadka kale dhex socdaan. Waxaa sidoo kale ay dowladiisu baadi goob ugu jirtaa guryo iyo dad hor leh oo cudurka uu aafeeyey .
Wadankaasi ayaa waxaa la rumaysan yahay inuu cudurka uu gaarsiiyey qof kasoo degay garoonka diyaaradaha.
Waxuu sheegay madaxweynaha wadankasi in Cudurkan uu dalkiisa la dagaalamayo isla markaasina virus kan uu yahay mid ka qara weyn in wadan kaliya uu la tacaalo.
Haddaba, maadaama ay waddanka Soomaaliya joogaa ciidamo ka socda waddanka Sera Leone oo ka tirsan howlgalka AMISOM kuwaasoo ay dhici karto in ay isugu dhex socdaan waddankooda iyo gudaha Soomaaiya, feejignaan intee la eg ayay AMISOM ka gashay arrintaasi, sideese looga hortagi karaa.
Wareysiyo arrintaas ku saabsan oo ay Caasho Ibrahim Aden iyo Maxamed Colaad Xasan la kala yeesheen Afhayeenka Amisom Corneel Cali Xaamud iyo Dr. Maxamed Cabdullahi Xaji Aaden oo xanuunka uur ku jirta ku taqasusay kana howl gala Isbitalka Regions magaalada Saint Paul ee Gobolka Minnesotta ka dhageyso xagga hoose.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2584381' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2584381.html' term='ebola'>
Dowladda oo Beenisay in Ebola Laga helay Somalia
Dowladda Somalia ayaa beenisay war ay baahisay mid ka mid ah idaacadaha Muqdisho oo sheegayay in qof ku nool Tuulada Buula-sharey ee gobolka Shabeelaha hoose laga helay cudurka Ebola.
Sii haya Wasiirka Caafimaadka ee Dowladda Federalka ee Somalia, Ali Mohamed Mohamud, oo shir jaraa’id maanta ku qabtay Magaalada Muqdisho ayaa sheegay in Somalia uusan ka jirin cudurkaasi Ebola, isagoo ku tilmaamay warkan ku tiri ku teen aan sal laheyn oo ay baahiyeen qaar ka mid ah warbaahinta.
Wasiirku waxuu sheegay in isla markii uu warkan soo baxay ay qaadeen talaabo deg deg si ey u karantiilaan qofka la tuhmay, hase yeeshee markii ay keeneen Muqdisho oo ay baaris ku sameeyeen ay dhabowday in qofkaasi aanu qabin xanuunka Ebola.
Ninkan oo lagu magacaabo , Abdulkadir Jinow Barow, ayaa ku wehliyay wasiirka shirka Jaraa’id.
Isagoo la hadlayay wariyeyaasha ayuu sheegay inuu dhawaan u safray dalka to Guinea, halkaas oo uu ganacsi ku heysto, isla markaana uu ku soo noqday Somalia 26kii bishii December ee ina dhaaftay.
Wuxuu sheegay in meelo badan oo uu soo maray lagu sameeyay baaris caafimaad oo la xiriirtay ka hor tagista fidista cudurka Ebola, hase yeeshee aan waxba laga helin.
Sii haya Wasiirka Caafimaadka ee Dowladda Federalka ee Somalia, Ali Mohamed Mohamud, ayaa intaasi ku daray in wasaaradda caafimaadka, ciidamada Booliska iyo wasaaradda cadaalada oo iskaashanaya ay baaryaan cidii ka dambeeysay fidinta warkan been abuurka ah, sharcigana la horkeeni doono.
Dhinaca kale, Ciidamo ka tirsan Nabad-Sugida dowlada Somalia ay xabsiga u taxaabeen agaasimihii, Tafaftirihii iyo mid kamid ah Shaqaalaha Idaacada Risaaala oo kamid ah idaacadaha FM ah ee ka howgala Magaalada Muqdisho.
Shaqaalaha idaacada ayaa sheegay in loo heysto warar la xariira qof laga shaki qabo inuu qabo cudurka Ebola oo gobolka shabeelaha hoose ay idaacadu ka wareystey.
Arintan ayaa ku soo beegmeysa iyado howlgalka Qaramada Midoobay ee la dagaalanka cudurka Ebola uu sheegay in fidistii ba’aneyd ee uu cudurka fidiyay laga yaabo in la soo afjaro sanadkan.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2602777' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2602777.html' term='ebola'>
Martida: Xoghayaha Guud ee Jimciyadda ICRC & IRC
Barnaamijkeena waxaa marti ku ah Xoghayaha Guud ee Jimciyadda ICRC & IRC, Ebola.Elhadj As Sy, Jimciyadaas oo ka mid ah ururada samafal ee sida weyn ugu howlan la dagaalanka cudurka Ebola ee ka dilaacay qaar ka mid ah dalalka ku yaala galbeedka Africa.
Barnaamijka oo uu Harun Macruuf ku wareysanayo Elhadj As Sy halka hoose ka dhageyso.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2491819' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2491819.html' term='ebola'>
Kulan Wacyigelinta Ebola oo Ka Dhacay Muqdisho
Xubno ka tirsan ururada bulshada rayidka ah ee Somaliyeed ayaa shalay kulan ay ku yeesheen magaalada Muqdisho, kaga hadlay sida dowladda Somalia iyo Howlgalka Midowga Africa looga baahanyahay inay ku baraarugsanaadaan ka hor tagista viruska Ebola ee faraha ba’an ku haya galbeedka Africa, inuu ku soo fido Somalia.
Inkastoo aan weli xanuunku soo gaarin gobolka geeska Africa, ayaa ururada bulshadu waxey sheegeen in somalia ay halis ugu jirto Ebola, maadaama dadlka Seire Leon oo ka mid ah sadexda dal ee galbeedka Africa ee uu Xanuunkan aafeeyay, ay ciidamo ka joogaan Somalia.
warbixin ku saabsan halka hoose ee qoraalkan ka dhageyso.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_1973372' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/1973372.html' term='ebola'>
Caalamka oo ka Tashanaya Daawada Ebola
Madaxweynaha Maraykanka Barack Obama ayaa sheegay inay waqti hore ay tahay in imika laga fikiro in daawada cusub ee la tijaabinayo ee loogu talagalay cudurka Ebola loo diro galbeedka Africa.
Madaxweynaha ayaa sidaasi ka sheegay gabagabada shirmadaxeedka Africa iyo Maraykanka, waxaana uu tilmaamay in loo baahanyahay in arrintaasi jawaabteeda laga sugo culimada sayniska eek u xeel dheer .
Daawadan ayaa la siiyay laba qof oo maraykan ah oo cudurkaasi ku dhacay.
Ha’yadda Caafimaadka Adduunka ee (WHO) ayaa sheegtay in ay todobaadka dambe qabanqaabinayso dood dhinaca anshaxa ah oo ku saabsan sida laga yeelayo dawadan cusub oo aan hore loo tijaabin oo loogu talagalay cudurka Ebola.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2413165' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2413165.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola: Korea oo Hakisey Duulimaadyada Africa
Shirkad kale oo diyaaradeed ayaa joojisey duulimaadyadeedii qaaradda Africa, xilli cudurka Ebola uu si xooggan ugu sii fidayo afar dal oo ku yaalla Galbeedka Africa.
Shirkadda Diyaaradaha ee Korea ayaa maanta sheegtay inay si ku meel gaar ah u hakin doonto duulimaadyada caasimadda Kenya ee Nairobi, tallaabadaas oo mas’uuliyiinta shirkadda ay ku tilmaameen inay tahay mid looga hortagayo fiditaanka xanuunka Ebola.
Ilaa iyo hadda ma jiro qof laga heley cudurka Ebola dalkaasi Kenya, balse Hay’adda Caafimaadka Adduunka ee WHO ayaa Kenya ku tilmaantey waddan khatar weyn ugu jira inuu xanuunkaasi ka dilaaco, sababo la xiriira dalka oo udub dhexaad u ah duulimaadyada diyaaradaha ee gobolka iyo qaaradda Africa inteeda kale.
Goor sii horeysey ayaa shirkadaha diyaaradaha ee British Airways iyo shirkadda diyaaradaha ee Imaaraadka waxay joojiyeen duulimaadyadoodii qeybo ka mid ah Galbeedka Africa, taas oo iyana ah tallaabo looga hortagayo fiditaanka Ebola.
WHO ayaa warbixinteedii dhowaan soo baxdey waxay ku xustey in dad gaaraya 1,069 ay sannadkan cudurka Ebola ugu dhinteen dalalka Guinea, Liberia, Nigeria iyo Sierra Leone. Ku dhowaad laba kun oo qof ayuu cudurkan ku asiibey waddamadan ku yaalla Galbeedka Africa.
Dadka uu dhowaan xanuunkan asiibey iyo kuwa maalmahn dhow u dhintey ayaa u dhashey Liberia iyo Sierra Leone.
Midowga Afrika ayaa bisha dambe dalka Burkina Faso ku qaban doona shir madaxeed looga hadlayo Ebola.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_4955742' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/4955742.html' term='ebola'>
Cudurka Ebola oo ka dillaacay dalka Uganda
Sarkaal ka tirsan wasaaradda caafimaadka dalka Uganda ayaa wakaaladda wararka ee AFP u sheegey in wiil yar oo shan jir ahaa uu maanta u dhintay cudurka Ebola, kaas oo maalmo ka hor laga helay cudurkaasi.
Kiiskaasi ayaa noqonaya kii ugu horreyey ee dalkaasi, tan iyo markii dalka ay deriska yihiin ee Jamhuuriyadda Dimuqraadiga Congo uu ka dillaacay cudurka.
Sarkaalka oo magaciisa ka gaabsaday in la shaaciyo, ayaa sheegey in wiilka uu xalay saq dhexe ku dhintay xarun lagu keligiis lagu baxnaaniyay, gudaha deegaanka Kasese.
Wasaaradda caafimaadka Uganda ayaa sheegtay Talaadadii in wiilka cudurka laga heley ay hooyadiis tahay Congolese, guursatay Ugandan.
Uganda ayaa sheegtay inay feejignaan sare uga jirtey cudurka Ebola, tan iyo markii uu ka dillaacay bariga dalka Congo, halkaas oo in ka badan 2 kun oo kiis laga diiwaan geliyay.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_3147077' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/cudurka-ebola-oo-dib-loogu-arkay-sierra-leone/3147077.html' term='ebola'>
Ebola Oo Dib Loogu Arkay Sierra Leone
WASHINGTON DC —
Sarkaal ku sugan dalka Sierra Leone ayaa sheegay in virus-ka cudurka Ebola laga helay meydka qof, maalin un kadib markii ururka caafimaadka adduunka ee WHO uu ku dhowaaqay in cudurka laga cirib tiray Galbeedka Afrika.
WHO, ayaa bayaan ku sheegtay Jimcaha (1/15/2016) inay xaqiijineyso kiiska cudurka Ebola e dalka Sierra Leone, oo laga helay meydka haweeney xanuunsatay kadibna geeriyootay horraantii bishan.
WHO, waxa ay sheegtay in shaac ka qaadistan ay macanaheedu tahay in la socosho xooggan iyo hab lagu jawaabi karo ay muhiim noqon doonaan bilaha soo socda, si la isugu diyaariyo suurta-galnimada ah in cudurka dib u dillaaco.
Khamistii, ayaa WHO waxa ay ku dhowaaqday dhammaanshaha cudurka Ebola ee dalka Liberia, taasi oo macanaheedu ahaa in dhamaman saddexdii dal ee xuddunta u ahaa cudurka ee Galbeedka Afrika ay iminka ka madax banaan yihiin cudurka.
Dhowaaqa WHO ayaa yimid kadib 42 maalmood oo wax kiisas cusub oo cudurka ah aan laga soo werin dalka Liberia.
Cudurka Ebola ee ka dillaacay Galbeedka Afrika ayaa galaaftay nolosha 11,000 oo qof, ayada oo in ka badan 28,000 oo qofna uu haleelay.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2564214' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2564214.html' term='ebola'>
Ciidanka Sierra Leon oo ka baxaya Somalia
Ciidamada ka socda waddanka Sierra Leone oo qayb ka ah howlgalka nabad ilaalinta AMISOM ee Soomaaliya ayaa lagu wadaa inay dalka ka baxaan oo ay dib ugu laabtaan waddankooda muddo bil gudaheed ah.
Kabixintaanka ciidamada Sierra Leone ayaa lagu sheegay inay ugu wacan tahay kaddib markii la waayay ciidamo waddankooda ka socda oo baddala sababo ay ugu wacan tahay cudurka Ebola.
Magaalada Kismaayo waxaa loogu qabtay xaflad sagootin ah oo dadkii ka qeybgalay uu ka mid ahaa Madaxweynaha Soomaaliya iyo wafdi uu hoggaaminayo. Maxamed Ismaaciil Shuuriye, kusimaha wasiir ku xigeenka wasaaradda howlaha guud oo ka mid ah wafdiga madaxweynaha ayaa Caasho Ibrahim uga warramay socdaalka wafdiga madaxweynaha.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2480794' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2480794.html' term='ebola'>
Garoonka JFK oo Dadka laga Baarayo Ebola
Garoonka diyaaradaha JFK ee magaalada New York City ayaa bilaabay baaris ku aadan cudurka Ebola oo lagu sameynayo rakaabka ka imanaya galbeedka Africa.
Shaqaalaha caafimaad ee ka qeyb qaadanaya barnaamijkan ayaa adeegsanaya qalab caafimaad, iyagoo su'aallo weydiinaya dadka ka yimaada galbeedka Africa eeGuinea, Liberia, iyo Sierra Leone iyo dalalka ku dhow dhow.
Baaritaan kuwan la mid ah ayaa laga bilaabayaa garoomada diyaaradaha Newark, New Jersey; Dulles Washington, Chicago iyo Atlanta.
Shantan garoon waxaa adeegsada 90 boqolkiiba rakaabka Mareykanka ka soo gala dalalka uu Ebola ka jiro ee Galbeedka Africa.
WHO waxey sheegtay in ku dhawaad 8,400 oo qof uu ku dhacay viruska la diwaan geliyay ilaa iyo toddoba wadan, in kabadan 4 kunna ay u dhinteen cudurka.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2620203' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2620203.html' term='ebola'>
Shir Madaxeedka AU oo Saakay ka Furmaya Addis Ababa
Shir madaxeedka 24aad ee Madaxweynayaasha ururka Midowga Africa ayaa saakay ka furmaya magaalada Addis Ababa ee caasimadda Ethiopia.
Madaxweynayaasha iyo masuuliyiin kale oo matalaya dalalka xubnaha ka ah ururka Midnimada Africa ee AU, oo uu ku jiro Madaxweynaha Somalia Xassan Sheikh Maxamuud ayaa ka qeyb galaya shirkan .
Inkastoo hal ku dhegga shir madaxeedka sanadkan 2015ka uu yahay xoojinta dumarka, ayaa haddana colaadda meelo kala duwan oo qaaradda ah ka jirta,, gaar ahaan gacan ka hadalka kooxda Boko Xaram ee dalka Nigeria, iyo dadaalada loogu jiro xakameynta cudurka Ebola ay yihiin agendayaasha ugu waaweyn ee shir madaxeedka.
Shalayna waxaa magaalada Addis Ababa ka dhacay shir ay lahaayeen madaxweynayaasha urur goboleedka IGAd.
Shirkaas oo ay albaabada u xiraayeen waxaa agendaha looga hadlayay uu ahaa xaaladda Suudaanta Koonfureed.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2477692' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2477692.html' term='ebola'>
USA: Thomas Duncan oo u Dhintay Cudurka Ebola
Xaaladda ugu horeysay ee cudurka Ebola ee laga helay dalka Maraykanka ayaa qofkii cudurka qabay uu Arbacadii shalay ku dhintay magaalada Dallas, gobolka Texas ee dalka Maraykanka.
Cisbitaalka Texas Health Presbyterian ayaa sheegay in Thomas Eric Duncan uu dhintay 10 maalmood ka dib markii cisbitaalka la seexiyey. Waxa uu magaalada Dallas yimid 20kii bishii September, isaga oo ka yimid dalkii uu u dhashay ee Liberia.
Madaxa Xarunta Xakameynta iyo Ka-hortagga Cudurada ee Maraykanka Dr. Thomas Frieden ayaa sheegay in uu aad uga xumaaday dhimashada Mr. Duncan. Mr. Frieden waxa uu sheegay in Maraykanku uuna ka marnaan karin cudurkan inta uu ka sii jiro Galbeedka Afrika.
Madaxweynaha Maraykanka Barack Obama ayaa sheegay in la dagaalka cudurka Eboa ay tahay arrin amni qaran oo mudnaan leh. Waxa uu sheegay in hanaan wax lagu baarayo oo cusub la dhaqan galin doono, kaas lagu sameyn doono dadka ka imanaya dalalka Guinnea, Liberia, iyo Sierra Leone ee imanaya dalka Maraykanka.
Mr. Obama ayaa sheegay in Maraykanku uu leeyahay dhakhaatiirta dunida ugu wanaagsan, kuwaas oo garanaya sida loola tacaalo cudurada faafa. Waxa uu sheegay inuu kalsooni ku qabo in cudurkani uuna ku faafi doonin dalka Maraykanka gudihiisa.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_1969763' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/1969763.html' term='ebola'>
WHO: Khatarta Ebola Way Sii Ballaaraneysaa
Agaasimaha Guud Hay’adda Caafimaadka Adduunka ee WHO ayaa u sheegtay madaxweyneyaasha Galbeedka Afrika ee waddamadooda uu haleeley cudurka Ebola in faafitaanka xanuunkan uu si xawli leh ku socdo, uuna ka dheereynayo dadaalada la doonayo in lagu xakameeyo.
Dr. Margaret Chan, Agaasimaha Guud ee WHO ayaa sheegtay in haddii faafitaanka uu faraha ka sii baxo, natiijada ka dhalan kartaa ay noqon karto mid aad u daran sida in dhimasho badan laga dhaxlo, dhaqaalaha iyo nolosha bulshadan ay wiiqmaan.
Dr. Chan waxay ku sugan tahay magaalada Conakry, halkaas oo maanta ay kula kulantey madaxweyneyaasha Guinea, Sierra Leone, Liberia iyo Ivory Coast.
WHO iyo hoggaamiyayaasha Galbeedka Afrika ayaa ku guda jira hirgelinta qorshe ku kacaya 100 milyan oo dollar oo lagula dagaalamayo faafitaanka Ebola, cudurkaas oo ila ahaatan dilay dad gaaraya 730.
Dr. Chan waxay sheegtay in shaqaale caafimaad oo tiradooda ka badan tahay 60 ay ka mid yihiin dhibaneyaasha uu cudurkaan haleeley una dhintey, isla markaana ay jiraan shaqaale ka tirsan kuwa samafalka caalamiga oo iyaguna xanuunkan qaadey.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2406336' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2406336.html' term='ebola'>
Sirleaf: Waan ka Hortageynaa Ebola
Madaxweynaha Liberia Ellen Johnson Sirleaf ayaa ku dhawaaqdey xaalad deg deg ah iyadoo xanuunka Ebola uu si xawli ah u galaafanayo nolosha boqolaal qof oo Liberian ah iyo dalalka kale ee ku yaalla Galbeedka Africa.
Khudbad ay shacabka u jeedisey maalintii Arbacada ayay Mrs. Sirleaf ku xustey in Liberia ay khasab tahay inay qaaddo talaabooyon kheyrul caadi ah oo lagu badbaadinayo nolosha shacabka iyo badbaadinta qaranka.
Talaabooyinka la qaadayo ayaa waxaa ka mid ah in ciidamada amniga loo adeegsado inay karantiin ama xeyndaab ku sameeyaan goobaha uu cudurka ka dilaacaya lana xakameeyo dhaqdhaqaaqa dadka.
Wakaaladda wararka ee Reuters ayaa sheegtay in booliska iyo ciidamada qalabka sida ee Sierra Leone ay go’doomiyeen goobaha miyiga, dadaal la doonayo in lagu xakameeyo faafitaanka cudurka Ebola ee waddanka.
Hay’adda Caafimaadka Adduunka ee WHO ayaa sheegaysa in xanuunka Ebola uu Galbeedka Afrika ku diley in ka badan 930 qof, una badan dalalka Liberia, Sierra Leone iyo Guinea. Dadka xanuunkan qaadey ayaa tiraddooda guud ay tahay 1,700.
Dhanka kale WHO ayaa sheegtay in toddobaadka dambe ay qaban doonto kulan looga hadlayo tijaabooyinka dawada Ebola.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2443454' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2443454.html' term='ebola'>
USA: Ruux Kale oo Laga Daweynayo Ebola
Isbital ku yaalla Mareykanka ayaa isku diyaarinayaa inuu daweeyo qofkii 3aad ee u dhashey Mareykanka ee xanuunka Ebola ka qaadey Galbeedka Africa.
Emory University Hospital oo ku yaalla Atlanta ayaa sheegay inuu rajeynayo in bukaankaasi uu maanta soo gaaro.
Hase yeeshee isbitalku maanu shaacin magaca qofkan bukaanka ah.
Bishii hore isbitalkan waxaa uu ku guuleystey inuu daweyo laba ruux oo ka mid ah shaqaalaha samafalka oo cudurka Ebola ka qaadey dalka Liberia.
Gobolka Nebraska ayaa waxaa lagu daweynayaa ruuxii afraad ee American ah oo uu ku dhacay xanuunka Ebola.
Xanuunka Ebola ayaa tan iyo markii uu ka dilaacay Galbeedka Afrika waxaa uu dalalka Guinea, Sierra Leone, Liberia iyo Nigeria ku diley in ka badan 2,000 oo qof.
Hay’adda Caafimaadka Adduunka ee WHO ayaa shaley sheegtay in virus-ka Ebola uu si xawli ah oo xoog badan ugu fidayo Liberia, isla markaana la filayo in toddobaadyada soo socda ay kumanaan qof oo kale qaadi doonaan.
Kala bar dadka ku qaadey xanuunkan iyo kuwa u dhintey ayaa u dhashey dalka Liberia.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_3071925' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/3071925.html' term='ebola'>
Cudurka Ebola Oo Dib Loogu Arkay Liberia
Saraakiil caafimaad ayaa sheegay in wiil da’ yar uu u dhintay cudurka Ebola gudaha Liberia, kaas oo noqoneya kiiskii ugu horreeyay ee cudurkaasi ku dhawaad muddo lix bilood ah oo uu qof u dhinto.
Wiilkan oo 15 jir ahaa, ayaa cudurkaasi looga helay duleedka bari ee caasimadda Manrovia isbuucii laga soo tagay. Aabihii iyo walaalkiisa ayaa sidoo kale la sheegay inay Ebola la xanuunsan yihiin hadda, waxana lagu hayaa xarun caafimaad oo duleedka Manrovia ah iyaga iyo seddex ruux oo kale oo qoyska ka tirsan.
Saraakiisha Liberia, ayaa si gaar ahaaneed ula socda 150 qof oo looga shakisan yahay inay halis u yihiin cudurkaasi, kuwaas oo ay ku jiraaan shaqaale caafimaad iyo dad kale oo xiriir la sameeyay qoyska.
Kiisaska cusub ee Ebola, ayaa dhabar jab ku ah waddanka Galbeedka Afrika ku yaalla, kaas oo hore u sheegay in cudurkaasi uu ka dhammaaday waddanka.
Bishii September 3-deedii ayaa la xaqiijiyay in Liberia uu cudurkaasi ka dhammaadey, inkastoo May 9-keeda uu ururka caafimaadka adduunka ee WHO sheegay in Ebola uu dalkaasi ka dhammaaday, ayaa haddana mar kale waxa la arkey Kiisas cusub oo cudurkaasi ah bishii June ee la ga soo gudbay.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2492157' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2492157.html' term='ebola'>
R/W Abdiweli oo ka Hadley Cudurka Ebola
Raiisul Wasaaraha Somalia Abdiweli Sheikh Ahmed ayaa sheegay in Midowga Afrika ay kala shaqeynayaan in si taxaddar leh loo hubiyo caafimaadka ciidamada AMISOM eek a imanaya waddamada uu sida xun u aafeeyey cudurka Ebola.
Raiisul Wasaaraha ayaa hadlakan ka jeediyey magaalada Muqdisho isagoo ka soo laabtey socdaal uu ku tegey waddamada Burundi iyo Kenya.
Dhanka kale Hay’adda Caafimaadka Dunida ee WHO ayaa shir deg deg ah ku qaban doonta magaalada Geneva, kaas oo looga hadli doono xanibaadaha dhanka socdaalka iyo baaritaanada caafimaad ee lagu sameynayo garoomada diyaaradaha kadib faafitaanka cudurke Ebola.
Magaalada Muqdisho waxaa warbixintan ka soo direy weriyaha VOA Hassan Kafi Abdirahman Qoyste.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2415993' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2415993.html' term='ebola'>
Kenya oo ka Gaashaamanaysa Ebola
Dawladda Kenya ayaa sheegtay inay dalkeeda soo gali karin dadka ka imanaya dalalka Guinea, Liberia iyo Sierra Leone oo ah dalalka uu ka dilaacay xanuunka Ebola.
Wasiirka Caafimaadka ee Kenya ayaa sheegay in go’aankan uu ku salaysanyahay xogt ay ka heleen hay’adda caafimaadka adduunka ee WHO.
Hay’adda ayaa sheegtay in caalamku uu dhayalsaday halista xanuunka Ebola, waxaanay hay’addu intaasi ku dartay in dhibaatada xanuunkaasi ay sii socon karto wakhtiyada soo socda.
Wasiirka Caafimaadka ee Kenya ayaa sidoo kale sheegay in xayiraaddan ku meel gaarka ah ay ka dhaqan galayso dhammaan garoomada diyaaradaha iyo xuduudaha dalka Kenya.
Shirkadda diyaaradaha ee Kenya Airways ayaa ku biirtay shirkado kale oo hakiyay amma shuruudo dheeraad ah ku soo rogay duulimaadyada tagaya galbeedka Africa.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_4961917' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/4961917.html' term='ebola'>
Kenya: Sadex qof oo looga shakisan yahay cudurka Ebola
Ilaa sadex ruux ayaa si gooni loogu karantiilay kadib markii dadkaasi looga shakiyay inay la xanuunsan yihiin caalaamadaha cudurka waayadaan dambe ku baayay Qaarada Africa ee Ebola, waxaana Sadexdaan qof lagu hayaa Isbitaalka magaalo madaxda Ismaamulka Kericho ee Kericho.
Sayga qofka dumarka ah ee lagu arkay calaamadaha cudurka iyo labo qof oo kale ayaa habeenkii Axadda la gaarsiiyay Isbitaalka.
Dr Shadrack Mutai, oo ah madaxa qeybta caafimaadka deegaanka ayaa warbaahinta u sheegay inay qaadeen tilaabooyin ay uga hortagi karaan calaamado loo malaynayo inay yihiin kuwa cudurka Ebola.
Deegaanada laga soo sheegayo in lagu arkay cudurka Ebola ee Kenya ayaa xaduud dhow la leh dalka Uganda oo maalmihii la soo dhaafay dhowr qof ay ugu geeriyoodeen cudurka Ebola, waxaana laga cabsi qabaa in tirada dhimashada cudurkaasi uu sababay ay sii kororto dalka Uganda.
Hay'adda Caafimaadka Adduunka ee (WHO) ayaa khuburo dhanka caafimaadka ah u dirtay Ismaamulka Kericho ee dalka Kenya si ay baaritaano dheeraad ah ugu soo sameeyaan sadexda ruux ee sida ee looga shakisan yahay inay qabaan calaamadaha cudurka.
Sidoo kale qeybta Adeega baaritaanka Dawooyinka ee Dowladda Kenya oo iyaguna tibaajabo ka qaaday dhiggaga dadkaan ayaa la filayaa in jawaabtooda ay soo saaraan saacadaha soo socda.
Maalintii Axadda ayay ahayd markii Isbitaalka Siloam loola cararay qof Haweeneey ah oo ka soo safarta magaalada Malaba ee Ismaamulka Busia ee dhanka Bari ee xuduuda Kenya iyo Uganda taasoo markii dambe loo soo wareejiyay Isbitaalka magaalada Kericho.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2494646' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2494646.html' term='ebola'>
Xaalad Cusub oo Cudurka Ebola oo laga Helay NY
Magaalada New York ee dalka Maraykanka ayaa waxa laga helay xaalad cusub ee cudurka Ebolaha. Dhakhtar dhawaan soo daweeyey dad qaba cudurka Ebola ee dalka Guinea ayaa isna laga helay cudurka, haatan lagu baaryaaa cusbitaala ku yaala New York.
Dhakhtarka oo lagu magacaabo Graig Spencer ayaa baaritaano bilow ah oo lagu sameeyey ay muujiyeen inuu cudurku hayo. Baarista ayaa ka dhacday cusbitaalka Bellevue ee gobolka New Yorking.
Xarunta ka hortaga iyo xakameeynta cudurada ee (CDC) ayaa waxay sameeyn doontaa baaritaankii labaad si ay si buuxda ugu cadeeyso natiijada baarista.
Gelinkii hore ee shalay oo khamiis ahayd ayaa Dr. Spencer uu ku wargeliyay ha’yadda dhakhaatiirta aan xuduuda lahayn oo uu uga shaqeynayay dalka Guinea in uu isku arkay qandho badan iyo lalabo oo labaduba ka mid ah astaamaha cudurka Ebola.
Saraakiil ka tirsan gobolka New York ayaa sheegay in Dr. Spencer uu arbacadii raacay tareen, isla markaana uu taksi u qaatay gurigiisa. Saraakiisha ayaa raadinaya cid kasta oo xiriir la sameysay dhakhtarka. Dr. Spencer wuxuu noqonayaa qofkii afraad ee laga helo cudurka isagoo ku sugan gudaha dalka Maraykanka.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_2471184' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/2471184.html' term='ebola'>
USA oo la Tacaaleysa Ebola
Mas’uuliyiinta caafimaadka dowladda dhexe ee Mareykanka iyo kuwa gobolka Texas ayaa goob gaar ah ku xanibey afar ruux oo ehel la ah nin dhowaan laga heley xanuunka Ebola, iyadoo mas’uuliyiinta Liberia ay sheegeen inay dacwad ku soo oogi doonaan been uu sheegey markii uu buuxinayey waraaqihiisii ee garoonka diyaaradaha xilli uu ka soo dhoofayey.
Bukaankan oo magaciisa la yiraahdo Thomas Duncan, una dhashey Liberia ayaa xaalad khatar ah ku sugan isbitalka magaalada Dallas.
Mas’uuliyiinta Liberia waxay sheegeen inay Duncan dacwad ku soo oogi doonaan, iyagoo ku eedeynaya inuu ka been sheegey markii la weydiiyey su’aal ah inuu horey ula kulmey ama u taabtey ruux qaba xanuunka Ebola.
Duncan ayaa ku jawaabey “Maya” iyadoo sida la og yahayna uu horey u caawiyey haweeney uur leh oo qabta Ebola, taxi-na uu saarey.
Dhanka kale isla dalka Liberia, filim qaade u dhashey Mareykanka oo u shaqeeya televishanka NBC ayaa waxaa ku dhacay xanuunka Ebola.
Televishanka ayaa sheegay inay dib dalka ugu soo celineyso dhammaan shaqaalihii halkaa ka joogey, isla markaana muddo 21 maalmood ah meel gaar ah lagu hayn doono.
</doc>
<doc docid='voa_3128339' lang='som' type='mono' source_url='https://www.voasomali.com/a/ethiopia-kismayo/3128339.html' term='ebola'>
Cidamada Itoobiya oo La Geeyey Kismaayo
Ciidamo gaaraya ilaa 250 askari oo hordhac ah oo ka socda dalka Itoobiya ee qaybta ka ah howlgalka AMISOM ayaa soo gaadhay magaalada Kismaayo.
Ciidamada Itoobiyaanka ee la geeyey magaalada Kismaayo ayaa qeyb ka ah ku dhowaad kun askari oo baddali doona ciidamadii Siralyoon ee qeybta ka ahaa howlgalka AMISOM eek a baxay Soomaaliya sida ay ilo xogogaal ah u sheegeen idaacadda VOA.
Ciidamadii Siralyoon ayaa Soomaaliya isaga baxay bishii Janaayo ee sanadkii 2015 sababo la xidhiidhay xaalad dhanka caafimaadka ah oo xiligaasi ka jirtay dalkaasi oo ka mid ahaa waddamada Galbeedka Afrika ee uu ka jiray cudurka Ebola oo suurtogelin waayey in la beddelo ciidanka.
Masuuliyiin ka tirsan maamulka Jubbaland ayaa VOA u xaqiijiyay in 250 askari ee yimid ay ku jiraan saraakiisha hogaamin doonta Ciidamada Itoobiyaanka ee AMISOM ee magaalada Kismaayo.
Sidoo kale masuulyiinta ayaa intaasi ku daray in ciidamada Itoobiyaanka, kuwa Kenya iyo kuwa Maamulka Jubbaland ay dhowaan qaadi doonaan howlgallo ka dhan ah kooxda Al-shabaab ee maamusha, degmooyinka, Jilib, Jamaame, Xagar, Bu'aale iyo deegaano kale sida ay hadalka u dhigeen.
Ciidamada Itoobiyaanka ayaa fariisimo ka samaystay garoonka diyaaradaha magaalada Kismaayo, dekadda iyo waqooyiga magaalada halkaasoo markii hore saldhigyo ciidan ku lahaayeen ciidamada Kenya iyo kuwa Wadanka Siralyoon.
Sidoo kale dekadda magaalada Kismaayo waxaa ku soo xirtay markab sida gaadiid iyo hub ay lee yihiin Ciidamada Itoobiya ee gaaray magaalada Kismaayo.
Dalka Soomaaliya waxaa jooga ciidamo AMISOM ah oo ka kala socda waddamada Yuganda, Burundi, Jabuuti iyo Itoobiya.
Ergayga gaarka ah ee Qaramada Midoobay ee xilkiisu ka dhammaaday Nick Kay ayaa VOA u sheegay in dabayaaqada sannadkan dib u eegis lagu samayn doono hawlgalka Midowga Afrika ee Soomaaliya, waxaana uu ku baaqayaa in si weyn diradda loo saaro dhammaystirka dhismaha ciidan Soomaaliyeed.
</doc>
